<li id="cite_note-Thorp_talk-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Thorp_talk_1-0" title="">^</a></b> E. O. Thorp, <cite>Fortune's Formula: The Game of Blackjack</cite>, American Mathematical Society, January 1961</li>
